 the completion\n$\\Lambda_i^{\\underline{x} R}(X), i \\in \\mathbb{Z},$ is a certain Koszul\ncohomology and Koszul homology resp. This provides new approaches to the right\nderived functor of torsion and the left derived functor of completion with\nvarious applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Mar 2020 15:03:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-19"}
